languages.text: "Что... что это значит? Неужели Вольный Торговец опустил{mf|ся|ась} до того, чтобы завести нас с Дитя в ловушку?" {n}Посланница гневно кривит губы.{/n} "Не стоило Великому Регенту Ааронто {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}доверять вам{/d}!"

languages.text: "What... what does this mean? Has the Rogue Trader stooped so low as to lure the Child and us into a trap?" {n}The envoy's lips curl in fury.{/n} "Great Regent Aaronto was wrong to {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}trust you{/d}!"

languages.text: “这……这是什么意思？莫非行商浪人已经堕落到了这种程度，把我们和圣子引诱到了陷阱里吗？”{n}特使愤怒地翘着嘴唇。{/n}“阿伦托摄政王当初真不该{d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}相信你{/d}！”
languages.original_text: "What... what does this mean? Has the Rogue Trader stooped so low as to lure the Child and us into a trap?" {n}The envoy's lips curl in fury.{/n} "Great Regent Aaronto was wrong to {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}trust you{/d}!"

languages.text: « Que... que se passe-t-il ? {mf|Le libre-marchand|La libre-marchande} se serait-{mf|il abaissé|elle abaissée} à nous attirer, l'Enfant et nous, dans un piège ? » {n}En proie à une terrible colère, l'émissaire retrousse les lèvres.{/n} « Le vénérable régent Aaronto a eu tort de {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}vous faire confiance{/d} ! »
languages.original_text: "What... what does this mean? Has the Rogue Trader stooped so low as to lure the Child and us into a trap?" {n}The envoy's lips curl in fury.{/n} "Great Regent Aaronto was wrong to {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}trust you{/d}!"

languages.text: «¿Qué...? ¿Qué significa esto? ¿Acaso {mf|el|la} Comerciante Independiente se ha rebajado a atraernos a la niña y a nosotros a una trampa?». {n}Los labios de la enviada se curvan de ira.{/n} «¡El gran regente Aaronto cometió un error al {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}confiar en usted{/d}!».
languages.original_text: "What... what does this mean? Has the Rogue Trader stooped so low as to lure the Child and us into a trap?" {n}The envoy's lips curl in fury.{/n} "Great Regent Aaronto was wrong to {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}trust you{/d}!"

traits.locale_text: «¿Qué...? ¿Qué es todo esto? ¿Acaso {mf|el|la} Comerciante Independiente se ha rebajado a atraernos a la niña y a nosotros a una trampa?». {n}Los labios de la enviada se curvan de ira.{/n} «¡El gran regente Aaronto cometió un error al confiar en usted!».

languages.text: "Was ... was bedeutet das? Ist {mf|der Freihändler|die Freihändlerin} so tief gesunken, das Kind und uns in eine Falle zu locken?" {n}Die Lippen des Gesandten verziehen sich vor Wut.{/n} "Der Große Regent Aaronto hätte Euch nicht {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}trauen{/d} dürfen!"
languages.original_text: "What... what does this mean? Has the Rogue Trader stooped so low as to lure the Child and us into a trap?" {n}The envoy's lips curl in fury.{/n} "Great Regent Aaronto was wrong to {d|Encyclopedia:CassiaQ1_RegenAlive}trust you{/d}!"
